 friends won&#8217;t stand for it.\u00a0\u00a0 So I use things like a filtered RSS feed to alert my followers of new blog posts, and I actually do interact with it (unlike some services).<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">I&#8217;m not asking for a cookie, I&#8217;m just having a random rant.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">See you all on <a href=\"http:\/\/www.twitter.com\">Twitter<\/a>&#8230;.tweet&#8230;tweet<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>I&#8217;m a Twitter addict.\u00a0 I&#8217;m not going to be apologetic about it.\u00a0 I love twitter.\u00a0 I&#8217;ll be happier when the rewrite occurs and it becomes a stable messaging platform.\u00a0\u00a0 The problem I have is balancing &hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":97594,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[2],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2898"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2898"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2898\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/97594"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2898"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2898"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http